- know the trends in the development of the digital economy;
- know the conceptual documents of the Russian Federation in the field of information security.
Skills:
- Be able to participate and plan in research and development activities in the field of information security
Skills:
- determine the priorities of their activities based on the prevailing prospects for the development of information security systems;
- to carry out an analysis of trends and prospects for the development of the field of information security in order to carry out research work aimed at obtaining new scientific and practical results.

